    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I think you dislike getting a whole line while you only have distinct data points.</p>\n<p>This is likely a feature of Grafana called Line interpolation. See configurable options here: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/panels-visualizations/visualizations/time-series/#line-interpolation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/panels-visualizations/visualizations/time-series/#line-interpolation</a></p>\n<p>If you do not like that, maybe you need to switch to another kind of visualization.</p>\n"
  } ],
